{"about_the_game":"<i>A strange visitor in a family. <br>Since they've come, none of them can continue living as they did. <br>Who was that visitor? <br>Could they be divine?</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A strange visitor.</h2>In DIVINITY, you play as a strange visitor in a family. Your mysterious appearance has ignited desires in each of the family members. With your divine gifts, you can help them to achieve their desires and reach divinity.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/familyphoto.png?t=1668912962\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Infatuate family members.</h2>Spend time with family members as they engage in activities throughout the estate, and see how they display their feelings towards you. Day &amp; night cycles, randomized events and guests keep the estate interesting.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Divine sight.</h2>Use your divine sight to find the most infatuated family member. This will also show how close you are to revealing their desires.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/Untitled-1.gif?t=1668912962\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Manipulate time.</h2>Use your powers to speed up time and see how their infatuation with you changes.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/DivinityMode.gif?t=1668912962\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fulfil their desires.</h2>Each family member has a desire, which is a puzzle that you must successfully solve for them to be a step closer to reaching divinity.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/painting.gif?t=1668912962\" /><br><br><i>This game is based upon the 1968 film Theorem</i><br>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Maid","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2158820/3042e6cfd73b37732f2137e0be4051efe914