 reach divinity.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/familyphoto.png?t=1668912962\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Infatuate family members.</h2>Spend time with family members as they engage in activities throughout the estate, and see how they display their feelings towards you. Day &amp; night cycles, randomized events and guests keep the estate interesting.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Divine sight.</h2>Use your divine sight to find the most infatuated family member. This will also show how close you are to revealing their desires.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/Untitled-1.gif?t=1668912962\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Manipulate time.</h2>Use your powers to speed up time and see how their infatuation with you changes.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/DivinityMode.gif?t=1668912962\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fulfil their desires.</h2>Each family member has a desire, which is a puzzle that you must successfully solve for them to be a step closer to reaching divinity.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/extras/painting.gif?t=1668912962\" /><br><br><i>This game is based upon the 1968 film Theorem</i><br>","developers":["Sejadasi"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158820/header.jpg?t=1668912962","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Ubuntu 20.04, Ubuntu 18.04, and CentOS 7<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> X64 architecture with SSE2 instruction set support<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM